---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
---

<h1>11ty + Decap CMS Demo</h1>
<p>This is a practice site. You’ll add articles via <code>/admin</code>.</p>

<div class="card">
  <h2>Next step</h2>
  <p>Deploy to Netlify and enable the CMS admin panel.</p>
</div>

<h2>Latest Articles</h2>

{% if collections.posts and collections.posts.length %}
  {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
    {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
      <article class="card">
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>

        {% if post.data.description %}
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% if post.data.featured_image %}
          <img
            src="{{ post.data.featured_image }}"
            alt=""
            style="max-width:100%; border-radius:12px; margin-top:12px;"
          />
        {% endif %}
      </article>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}

  <p><a href="/articles/">View all articles →</a></p>
{% else %}
  <p>No articles yet.</p>
{% endif %}